step-by-step:

* be root
* cfdisk
* mkfs.ext2
* mount target partition to /mnt/lfs
* mkdir /mnt/lfs/tools && ln -svf /mnt/lfs/tools /tools
* cd toolchain
* build toolchain: execute each bee file and install it
(XXX.bee --no-archive-build && bee install XXX)
