* configure shadow:
pwvonc
grpconv
sed -i 's/yes/no/' /etc/default/useradd
passwd root

* make the system bootable:
logout
reenter_chroot.sh
cd ~/making_bootable
lfs-bootscripts-20111017-0.bee
modify /etc/fstab
build kernel: linux-3.1-0.bee
make bootable with grub
